Description of the table C_PIB_INSTALLED_PRODUCT_BUSINESS_PARTNER

20-Nov_2022

 

Partner from MP1 IHPA table for Equipment. IE03/IQ03 display partner from IHPA table.

 

Source: IHPA for OBJNR starting with 'IE'

 

Notes: EQUZ customer data does not always match to IHPA and is not exposed in SPC except in the technical table PIB_EQUZ.

Type field in IHPA does not always identify equipment so the object number is used as the filter.

 

Update Frequency: Daily created or changed rows in IHPA, also rows for equipment numbers in EQUI that are created or show a change. changes in Partner data do not always update the change dates in IHPA.
